title: DLSA Warangal Recruitment 2026 - Apply Online for Various Peon and Attendant Posts
description: District Legal Services Authority Warangal (DLSA Warangal) has released an official notification for the recruitment of 01 Office Peon/ Attendant  Posts. Those candidates who have qualified in the 10th Pass can grab this chance and apply for the DLSA Warangal Recruitment 2026. Here we include the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for these posts. Interested and eligible candidates can apply before the last date of application....
